metadata.name: Digital Paint 1
metadata.description:
Title: Digital Paint  
Artist: Godwits  
Year: 2023  
Smart Contract By: Manifold  
Artist Royalty: 10%  

"Digital Paint" is an innovative mixed-media artwork that combines the cutting-edge power of artificial intelligence with the timeless techniques of painting. This vivid and evocative collection seamlessly merges custom AI-generated imagery, digital paint, colors, and 3D elements with abstraction styles to create visual art for the senses.  

The abstract nature of the AI-generated painting invites the viewer to explore their own interpretations and emotions, making it a personal experience. The painting techniques are seamlessly incorporated into the artwork, blending harmoniously with the digital elements.  

The evolution of embracing AI as a tool can bring a new perspective on creative possibilities. AI-Collaborative work combining artificial intelligence with traditional art forms inspires a sense of wonder and awe at the endless potential of human creativity.   
 
*This is a dynamic collection so anything can happen in the future.  

Limited to personal non-commercial use and resale rights of NFT are granted.
